{
  "page": "Lister",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the Lannister guard, see <a href=\"/index.php/Lester\" title=\"Lester\">Lester</a>. For the Lord of Crow's Nest, see <a href=\"/index.php/Lester_Morrigen\" title=\"Lester Morrigen\">Lester Morrigen</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Lister</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Lister</b> was the brother of <a href=\"/index.php/Jack-Be-Lucky\" title=\"Jack-Be-Lucky\">Jack-Be-Lucky</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lennocks\" title=\"Lennocks\">Lennocks</a>. He was killed by the forces of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lister's brother <a href=\"/index.php/Jack-Be-Lucky\" title=\"Jack-Be-Lucky\">Jack-Be-Lucky</a> recalls that Lister had been killed by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">the Lannisters</a>, and how losing his eye is nothing compared to that.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He later blames <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> for the deaths of Lister and another one of their brothers, <a href=\"/index.php/Lennocks\" title=\"Lennocks\">Lennocks</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 34\">Chapter 34</a>, Arya VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_22\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 22\">Chapter 22</a>, Arya IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403122352\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.106 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.383 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 540/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10597/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4625/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 310/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1260/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.260/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.73 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  373.241      1 -total\n 85.88%  320.538      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 85.33%  318.471      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.49%   42.893     12 Template:Infobox_value\n 10.53%   39.294      1 Template:For-multi\n 10.31%   38.480      1 Template:Hatnote\n  2.84%   10.589      2 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.74%   10.211      3 Template:Ref\n  2.20%    8.218      2 Template:Date\n  1.67%    6.249      3 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\